29:26.098 --> 29:28.667
They put the cross up there.

29:28.700 --> 29:31.303
So up there, you go
to see Christ.

29:31.337 --> 29:32.805
And take your selfie.

29:34.540 --> 29:37.343
But it's beautiful.
It's still beautiful.

29:37.376 --> 29:40.579
No, I've never seen
a place like this,

29:40.612 --> 29:43.282
